><div>{% if faq_3_answer != blank %}{{ faq_3_answer | metafield_tag }}{% else %}<p>Rotate toys weekly or whenever interest drops. Keep a mix of shredding, chewing, climbing, and foraging items so your bird has different activities throughout the week.</p>{% endif %}</div></details>\n    <details><summary>{{ faq_4_question }}</summary><div>{% if faq_4_answer != blank %}{{ faq_4_answer | metafield_tag }}{% else %}<p>Yes. If you are unsure what fits your bird, contact Squawk Shop with your bird's species, cage size, chewing style, and what you already own. We can help build a safer, more enriching setup.</p>{% endif %}</div></details>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .species-faq { max-width: 980px; }\n  .species-faq h2 { margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: clamp(24px, 3.4vw, 36px); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: 0; }\n  .species-faq__list { display: grid; gap: 10px; }\n  .species-faq details { border: 1px solid rgba(24,37,46,.14); border-radius: 8px; background: #fff; overflow: hidden; }\n  .species-faq summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; padding: 15px 18px; list-style-position: inside; }\n  .species-faq details > div { padding: 0 18px 16px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }\n  .species-faq details > div p { margin: 0; }\n</style>",
